ICANDELO LIKASEKELA-MPHATHISWA WEENTENGISO NORHWEBO: UBUME






UBUME

IINKONZO



UQHAGAMSHELWANO



ICandelo loSekela-Mphathiswa lilo elijongene nokuncedisana neCandelo loMphathiswa ngemigaqo-kqubo nokuqulunqwa kwemithetho emalunga nezorhwebo noshishino. ICandelo loSekela-Mphathiswa likwajongene:
* nokusungula imigaqo-nkqubo nemithetho yesizwe
* nokulungelelanisa imisebenzi yeSebe lezoRhwebo noShishino
* nokuqulunqa kwanokusungula imithetho
* nokuqhuba nayiphi na eminye imisebenzi yolawulo emiselwe kuMgaqo-siseko okanye kwimithetho yesizwe.
